Vendored TPC-H dbgen generator
==============================

The contents of third_party/gotpc/dbgen/ are derived from the `tpch/dbgen`
package of go-tpc (https://github.com/pingcap/go-tpc), which is licensed under
the Apache License, Version 2.0. A copy of that license is in
third_party/gotpc/LICENSE.

Modifications made by Stroppy (per Apache License §4(b), "carry prominent
notices stating that You changed the files"):

  - dbgen/*.go: removed the SQL/CSV `*sink.CSVSink`-based loader types,
    constructors, and the loader-driven genTbl/DbGen entry points, which
    depended on go-tpc's internal `pkg/sink`. Row generation logic (the
    make*/sd*/init* functions, the RNG streams, distributions, and text pool)
    is preserved verbatim.
  - dbgen/driver.go and the table files: the scale factor `scale` was changed
    from int64 to float64 to restore upstream dbgen's fractional scale-factor
    support (e.g. 0.01 for tests); the `base * scale` products that derive row
    counts and foreign-key ranges were updated to compute in float and floor to
    int64.
  - dbgen/api.go: NEW, Stroppy-authored. Exposes a minimal exported surface
    (EnsureInit, Reset, Seek, RowStart/RowStop, the Make* makers, row-count
    accessors, and a global generation mutex) so the pkg/datagen/tpchgen
    adapter can drive row production. Not part of upstream go-tpc.

